OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777406752
OL,3,CJimmy Kimmel defends Melania 'widow'
OL,4,Cjoke after Trumps call for his firing
OL,6,FLate-night TV host Jimmy Kimmel has
OL,7,Fdefended a joke he made about Melania
OL,8,FTrump last week after the first lady
OL,9,Fand US President Donald Trump both
OL,10,Fcalled for him to be fired.
OL,12,FKimmel performed a sketch on his
OL,13,Fprogramme, Jimmy Kimmel Live! on
OL,14,FThursday last week, in which he
OL,15,Fdescribed Melania as glowing "like an
OL,16,Fexpectant widow", in a reference to
OL,17,Fthe couple's 23-year age gap.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
