OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777406752
OL,3,CJimmy Kimmel defends Melania 'widow'
OL,4,Cjoke after Trumps call for his firing
OL,6,FThree days later, a gunman opened fire
OL,7,Fat White House correspondents' dinner
OL,8,Fin Washington DC in an alleged attempt
OL,9,Fto assassinate the president.
OL,11,FMelania was also in attendance and had
OL,12,Fto be evacuated alongside her husband.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
