FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777406752
OL,3,CJimmy Kimmel defends Melania 'widow'
OL,4,Cjoke after Trumps call for his firing
OL,6,F"It was a very light roast joke about
OL,7,Fthe fact that he's almost 80 and she's
OL,8,Fyounger than I am," Kimmel said during
OL,9,Fthe opening monologue of his Monday
OL,10,Fshow.
OL,12,F"It was not by any stretch of the
OL,13,Fdefinition a call to assassination,
OL,14,Fand they know that. I've been very
OL,15,Fvocal for many years, speaking out
OL,16,Fagainst gun violence in particular."
OL,26,@pD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
