PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777406752
OL,3,CJimmy Kimmel defends Melania 'widow'
OL,4,Cjoke after Trumps call for his firing
OL,6,FDuring the sketch last week, Kimmel
OL,7,Fpretended to deliver a routine for the
OL,8,FWhite House correspondents' dinner,
OL,9,Fwith the camera showing Melania on-
OL,10,Fscreen as he said: "Mrs. Trump, you
OL,11,Fhave a glow like an expectant widow."
OL,13,FHe then referenced Melania's upcoming
OL,14,F56th birthday, saying she would be
OL,15,Fcelebrating at home "the same way she
OL,16,Falways does - looking out a window and
OL,17,Fwhispering, 'What have I done?'"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777406752
OL,3,CJimmy Kimmel defends Melania 'widow'
OL,4,Cjoke after Trumps call for his firing
OL,6,FAfter the shooting on Saturday,
OL,7,FMelania described the sketch as
OL,8,F"hateful and violent rhetoric" that
OL,9,Fshe said was "intended to divide" the
OL,10,Fnation.
OL,12,F"His monologue about my family isn't
OL,13,Fcomedy- his words are corrosive and
OL,14,Fdeepen the political sickness within
OL,15,FAmerica," the first lady said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
