PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777406752
OL,3,CJimmy Kimmel defends Melania 'widow'
OL,4,Cjoke after Trumps call for his firing
OL,6,FTrump also posted about Kimmel on
OL,7,FTruth Social, calling the joke a
OL,8,F"despicable call to violence" and "far
OL,9,Fbeyond the pale" as he called for the
OL,10,Fhost to be fired.
OL,12,FKimmel said he agreed that "hateful
OL,13,Fand violent rhetoric is something we
OL,14,Fshould reject" during Monday's
OL,15,Fmonologue.
OL,17,FReferencing the first lady, he added:
OL,18,F"And I think a great place to start to
OL,19,Fdial that back would be to have a
OL,20,Fconversation with your husband about
OL,21,Fit."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
