FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777406752
OL,3,CJimmy Kimmel defends Melania 'widow'
OL,4,Cjoke after Trumps call for his firing
OL,6,F"I also should point out Donald Trump
OL,7,Fis allowed to say whatever he wants to
OL,8,Fsay, as are you and as am I and as are
OL,9,Fall of us, because under the First
OL,10,FAmendment we have as Americans the
OL,11,Fright to free speech," Kimmel
OL,12,Fcontinued.
OL,14,FThis isn't the first time Kimmel has
OL,15,Ffaced criticism from Trump over jokes
OL,16,Fmade during his show.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
