OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777406752
OL,3,CJimmy Kimmel defends Melania 'widow'
OL,4,Cjoke after Trumps call for his firing
OL,6,FIn September last year, the comedian
OL,7,Fwas briefly taken off air by ABC after
OL,8,Fsuggesting on his show that Trump and
OL,9,Fhis allies were capitalising
OL,10,Fpolitically on the murder of activist
OL,11,FCharlie Kirk.
OL,13,FAfter returning to air after a near
OL,14,Fweeklong suspension, Kimmel told
OL,15,Fviewers: "I have no illusions about
OL,16,Fchanging anyone's mind, but I do want
OL,17,Fto make something clear, because it's
OL,18,Fimportant to me as a human.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
